        TypeScript for type safety. A smaller portion of native mobile code is
        written in Java on Android and Objective-C/Swift on iOS to interface
        directly with third-party native SDK.
      </p>
      <p class="pb-1 text-justify indent-4 text-sm text-tapa-500">
